%B4ng-ch%C3%BAa-bi%E1%BB%87t-qu%C3%A1n-kh%E1%BB%95-v%C5%A9-t%E1%BA%B7ng-V%E1%BB%87-U%C3%BD-Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Khanh-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-rxiexbLoRqzGof6SLwTIcw">Ngọc Chân công chúa biệt quán khổ vũ tặng Vệ Uý Trương Khanh kỳ 1 - 玉真公主別館苦雨贈衛尉張卿其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-t%E1%BB%A9-th%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1-Kh%E1%BA%BF-t%E1%BB%A9-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-qjyFFM43hYrWKw3L9DkOXA">Tặng Vương nhị thập tứ thị ngự Khế tứ thập vận - 贈王二十四侍禦契四十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu%E1%BB%B5-Nguy%C3%AAn/Thi%C3%AAn-Thai-th%E1%BA%A1ch-l%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-h%E1%BA%ADu-quan-b%E1%BB%99c-b%E1%BB%91/poem-Vqow27pdQlBUwaSkG3-PNQ">Thiên Thai thạch lương hậu quan bộc bố - 天台石梁雨後觀瀑布</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu%E1%BB%B5-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-zQyjfkM-l-eVSsp11IFYtg">Nguỵ Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Di%C3%AAn-Ni%C3%AAn/V%C5%A9-l%C3%A2m-lang/poem-9r2SL8xFgZqdSMY2iLdnmA">Vũ lâm lang - 羽林郎</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Di%C3%AAn-Ni%C3%AAn/author-vxx2nHLFJhKIREop8LIMDg">Tân Diên Niên</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
